{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"荔乡三唱","authors":["关振东","林举英"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":8,"day":18}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"荔乡三唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林举英  关振东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“知了——知了”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“知了——知了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象笛子，高奏丰收调。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是荔乡盛大的节日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿红着绿，挂满富饶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里正在举行盛会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知了、知了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的生活酿出新醪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“知了——知了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清明后，几声呜咽几声叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴风惨惨草萋萋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷雨霏霏花果凋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椿象爬满树，群鸦啼夕照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知了、知了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四人帮”的屠刀把春光砍掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“知了——知了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对早霞，高歌长笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风又灌满园春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老树新枝俏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梢头一望大火烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知了、知了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严冬已过，艳阳正照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“挂绿”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘果的嫦娥对你深深赞赏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临走把一条玉带挂在你肩上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此“挂绿”美名四海传扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在姊妹中数你最漂亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仙女原想让你活得更美好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美好的境遇并没有从天而降。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阅三百载沧桑幻变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熬尽了多少雪雨风霜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会你被钉上铁丝网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整天见的是带刺的马梆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从丽日从海上跃出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你才沐到温暖的春阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海的碧波给了你绿带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东天的早霞给了你红裳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看梢头果红如火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一派热烈的南国风光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仙女没给你带来美好的年月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风为你送来似锦的韶光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这冰消雪融的火红时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美好事物都受到爱护赞扬……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荔枝堤抒情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁把青山扛来碧海中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在波心把春天播种？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵棵，一丛丛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠峰迭翠峰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，婆娑如盖的果树哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是拓荒者留下的帐篷？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帐篷温暖过一个个甜梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荔林谛听过多少情话喁喁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云团涌，烟霞笼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云霞绿映红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠圆玉润的红玛瑙哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是少先队野营的篝火熊熊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这春回大地的年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海也情怀激动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是红云霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是青翠峰……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}